name: Lushtemples — Ever uncaged
description:
Nature's beauty, is free 

—
The "Lushtemples" are a series of generative designs that attempt to capture the graphic density of the nature untamed ; the works remain aware of the un-natural process of re-creating nature with code, introducing some notes of artificiality and hints of the underlying technique, such as 3D meshes or destructive digital glitches.

Started as an experiment with "figurative generative" approach and pen plotters, the graphic style evolved into a more painterly style with timeless settings, while keeping its equation-based, line-art fundamentals.


— Generative drawing
— Made with original Javascript code
— Format PNG
— Resolution 6300x8910
